<item>
            <title>[FLINK-7818] Synchronize MetricStore access in the TaskManagersHandler</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-7818</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The &lt;tt&gt;TaskManagersHandler&lt;/tt&gt; accesses the &lt;tt&gt;MetricStore&lt;/tt&gt; when details for a single &lt;tt&gt;TaskManager&lt;/tt&gt; are requested. The access is not synchronized which can be problematic because the &lt;tt&gt;MetricStore&lt;/tt&gt; is not thread safe.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I propose to add synchronization.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
